premise_source_doc_sentence: Peter Jackson co-authored and co-edited several publications on big cats and tigers , including Wild Cats : Status Survey and Conservation Action Plan , compiled and edited by Kristin Nowell and Peter Jackson  (  IUCN 1996  )  , and Riding the Tiger : Tiger Conservation in Human Dominated Landscapes  (  Cambridge University Press 1999  )  .
